<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;As long as your premiums are paid when due, your TD 20-Year Term Life insurance will renew automatically for successive 20-year terms, with no medical examination required, providing continuous coverage until your 80th birthday. Premiums are fixed for each 20-year term and are guaranteed not to increase until each renewal date, regardless of your age or changes in your health.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
  <data key="d1">9.0</data>
