<node id="&lt;hyperedge&gt;&quot;Yes, you can convert to a permanent life insurance policy, with no medical questions, at any time up to and including the policy anniversary nearest the insured's 69th birthday. Of course, the premiums will depend on the type and amount of coverage chosen but, regardless of health, you cannot be turned down for coverage under this conversion option.&quot;">
  <data key="d0">hyperedge</data>
